ards the US Open set-up, which will place significant physical demands upon them.</p>\n\n<p>Stenson was quick to acknowledge such problems. The Swede said: &ldquo;It&rsquo;s tricky out there. You&rsquo;ve got to be careful. You see that yellow grass laying down? It&rsquo;s dangerous.&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p>Stenson told golfweek.com that he had witnessed a particularly bad fall by a scorer during a practice round at the start of US Open week. Unlike players, caddies don&rsquo;t wear spiked footwear, a move taken to protect greens but which raises questions on weeks such as these.</p>\n\n<p>Gallacher&rsquo;s management firm paid tribute to the medical assistance and back-up options provided by the USGA. A local caddie has been placed on standby for the Scottish Ryder Cup player, who is due to begin his US Open quest at 2.39pm local time on Thursday.</p>\n\";}}}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:1;}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:0;}','2015-06-18 15:17:32','2015-06-18 15:17:32',0,1000,'Element\\Text'),('18ca2afb8e3ae6bf6b42a7dc11b684a3',NULL,'','a:4:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;s:33:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Text\";}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;s:33:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Text\";}s:10:\"copyrights\";a:1:{i:0;s:33:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Text\";}s:5:\"image\";a:1:{i:0;s:34:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Image\";}}','a:4:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:33:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Text\";s:32:\"01257a95f32ea0bca50e3e9b4aada97a\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:33:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Text\";s:32:\"e801bc04e8f7cab3857e8077972d0b25\";}}s:10:\"copyrights\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:33:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Text\";s:32:\"a5ecc59a9780b37bad251d3b4ab35a5e\";}}s:5:\"image\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:34:\"BackBee\\ClassContent\\Element\\Image\";s:32:\"2e34a3b8fbf045212ab38ae911c49a16\";}}}','a:0:{}','a:4:{s:5:\"title\";i:1;s:11:\"description\";i:1;s:10:\"copyrights\";i:1;s:5:\"image\";i:1;}','a:4:{s:5:\"title\";i:0;s:11:\"description\";i:0;s:10:\"c