as also given a red card and will miss his side&rsquo;s final group game against Peru.</p>\n\n<p>&ldquo;It&rsquo;s never a good thing when at the end of a match we&rsquo;re talking about the referee,&rdquo; Dunga said. &ldquo;I think if you look at what happened, including at the end, you have to conclude it has something to do with the referee.</p>\n\n<p>&ldquo;There was a similar problem at a Corinthians match when the same referee was in charge,&rdquo; Dunga said, referring to a recent Libertadores Cup tie when Osses sent off two Corinthians players in a match against Paraguayan side Guarani. &ldquo;It&rsquo;s more than just coincidence.&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Asked how he would prepare for the Venezuela clash without Neymar, Dunga said: &ldquo;We&rsquo;ll think about that tomorrow. We&rsquo;ve played matches before without Neymar. We&rsquo;ll just to play in a way that makes up for his absence.&rdquo;</p>\n\";}}}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:1;}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:0;}','2015-06-18 09:47:37','2015-06-18 09:47:49',1,1001,'Element\\Text'),('7ae7290801e86f9629f582ec86de4cb7',NULL,'Title','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"scalar\";}}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:6:\"scalar\";s:170:\"&quot;We&#39;ve worked on eight citadel walls and four temples to prevent their collapse and decay, and cleared drains which remove subterranean water and humidity,&quot;\";}}}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:1;}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:0;}','2015-06-18 10:26:50','2015-06-18 10:27:46',1,1001,'Element\\Text'),('7af5177502c4e5ea86855bc637d4ba0c',NULL,'Title','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"scalar\";}}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:6:\"scalar\";s:149:\"&quot;I play my game. I try to do my best in every single match of the year and not try to be better if there is somebody or not on the crowd.&rdquo;\";}}}','a:0:{}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:1;}','a:1:{s:5:\"value\";i:0;}','2015-06-18 10:14:10','2015-06-18 10:14:32',1,1001,'Element\\Text'),('7bbf6d2818314d9d72b47c577a035e